messages.message: @dlluncor Anant’s suggestion re survey is good. Since A&P has been doing the UDFs, do you all have an inventory of what’s been created? Happy to assist in its creation if not.

@Balaram @Kerry @Mohamed could we create some kind of spreadsheet or catalog for the type of long-tsil capabilities that we have -- things like US Address, Name, Numerical format, Date, etc. Maybe maintaining a spreadsheet of this information for starters will help us catalog the function and in what setting can it be used?

Perhaps @Aaron Vontell and @Hari  can contribute any of their general functions since they've been thinking about this. @Balaram or @Kerry maybe you can take the lead on developing our long-tail catalog and @Mohamed can help in that process?
Yes of course - can I have until Monday to give everyone something as a starter? :slightly_smiling_face:

Sounds great to me. We're aiming to have these capabilities surfaced in Refiner V5 using a suggest API. One part of th puzzle is thinking through what information well need to know from the user to provide a useful and meaningful suggestion
Y’all rock. This will be a great asset to have even independent software efforts.
I will collate the ones I have as well :+1:
